{
  "stem": "15174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I looked down and I said you-- I said to my mother, I said, you know, that fishing boat that my-- that my aunts and cousin and my uncles were on, it looks like it's right next to our cabin.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Why don't we run down and see-- see if that's so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we ran down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We opened the porthole, and they were right there, right there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We didn't have to shout to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We-- we could talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I don't know which day it was after we had arrived but, anyway, our-- my aunts and uncles tried to reassure us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They said no, you know, the Jewish organizations are doing everything they can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You can't imagine that you're here, they're not going to let you get off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It'll just take another few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You know, you-- don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Everything will work out all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was wonderful, because we were able to see them close up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We were able to talk to them close up without screaming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But I remember, in spite of the fact that my relatives kept assuring us, my mother went back in the cabin, and she-- she got the gifts, a few little gifts that we had-- she had bought for my relatives in Cuba.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And she threw them into the boat and-- into the boat that they were in-- and she said, well, at least the gifts will arrive here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We might not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And of course, the mood on the boat was terrible during all this time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Somebody actually tried to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I mean, that-- you can-- you can imagine that that would be so.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
